{"tid":30253,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"富X證劵交易美股時出現懷疑....","createTime":"2016-12-09T05:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T22:44:51.000Z","uid":10606,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6425cb663da7dbf13faf7898d61444b3936e69f3","tid":30253,"uid":10606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">富X證劵交易美股時出現懷疑擅自更改交易紀錄，偽造文書，未經本人授權買入其他股票</span><br />\n<br />\n是咁的...見到港股咁on9....美股大升港女都跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...所以去富X牛牛開個美股戶口玩..貪佢可以少少地咁玩...1股1股買賣都得..<br />\n點知就出事...尋晚send左信去證監...等佢覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人於2016年12月7日晚於富X證劵交易美股時出現懷疑有人擅自更改交易紀錄，偽造文書，以求蒙混過關，現逐一申訴如下 :<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月7日晚，本人透過富X證劵看美股時，發現美股Under Armour (UA)值得投資，當時富x證劵交易程式（富X牛牛）顯示其價錢為USD$26.60，於是本人便透過富X證劵美股戶口交易50股Under Armour (UA)。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，本人一直用限價盤於USD$26.66，USD$26.68購買，但都未能買入。短短數分鐘Under Armour (UA)已由USD$26.66升到USD$27.03。於是，本人便用市價盤直接購入50股Under Armour (UA)。只見成交金額為USD$31.85，時間是2016年12月7日23時17分16秒。本人當時大感驚訝，帳面損失已是二百多美元，立即查看富X證劵交易程式，但程式上顯示Under Armour (UA)價錢仍是USD$27.00左右。<br />\n<br />\n於是從富X證劵軟件線上詢問有關人員，但他只回覆是正跟美國了解原因，叫我稍等。但本人急不及待，奈何欠缺任何資訊和情報下，只好以1股試試用市場盤放出，信息顯示是以USD$32.02成交，時間是2016年12月7日23時54分33秒。其後，本人無奈以欠缺任何可得知的信息下，也不知是獲利還是蝕放。最後以市場盤USD$32.02放出40股和USD$32.022放出9股Under Armour (UA)。<br />\n<br />\n2016年12月8日下午約4時，富X證劵職員雷X傑先生(持牌號碼：AYO3X2)終於致電本人，聲稱昨天本人交易之股票為 Under Armour, Inc. Class A (UAA)，並要求本人當昨天所發生的事情沒有發生，並會承擔交易中所產生的股票損失。本人於2016年12月8日晚上收到富x證券的日結單，居然顯示本人交易之股票是Under Armour, Inc. Class A (UAA)。<br />\n<br />\n講完...想問下巴絲...富x證券間野有無犯法..同可以點拎到賠償<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖後補"},{"pid":"a10556a6ad446b596dc4836cb633f07cccc96399","tid":30253,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f8eb59668037161f0a8535200eedd24e340687","tid":30253,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:44:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ba68a1f7385f5950d4a354a49ec572ab340e3c0","tid":30253,"uid":5329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719b5bdde89088973e62b6b7ae17570639deeb52","tid":30253,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"咁撚恐怖"},{"pid":"92fbc0d6e0f9cf2ff0dd71254c96856ea07117ba","tid":30253,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"推上報啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a91419bfd9b79d28e7d5b9d1578f271f7ec87bb","tid":30253,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c068b1669a1a7b0e527421c7c854b94489c637a","tid":30253,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"上證監玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114e7243d212bd9f9a23bf7e386d8083f2926393","tid":30253,"uid":10606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:51:25.000Z","msg":"UA 一直都係想入呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0n0jfa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0n0jfa7.jpg&h=b4c6658e&s={SI