s/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d31bbaa30ed9d09f5168c9647e0c650cd42eed","tid":30253,"uid":61755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實成單野係無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但又真係有位入佢喎。。<br />\n<br />\n有位入緊係要入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身就唔會對報價付責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果一刻係買賣緊UA<br />\n而唔係UAA<br />\n亦都無諗過入UAA<br />\n而佢個報價系統亦顯示係UA</blockquote><br />\nOK 我明了<br />\n岩岩我搞錯左<br />\n<br />\n件事其實係咁<br />\n近日UA Class C (UA.C)改左代號轉左做 UA<br />\nUA Class A (UA) 就改左代號做 UAA<br />\n而睇個圖表 佢就咁寫係Under Armour咁即係代表買UA 既C Class<br />\n但個系統有問題 就照落左UA Class A"},{"pid":"2b46c71517cbbca2fdb5c506a37ace970c5a146f","tid":30253,"uid":10606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身就唔會對報價付責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果一刻係買賣緊UA<br />\n而唔係UAA<br />\n亦都無諗過入UAA<br />\n而佢個報價系統亦顯示係UA</blockquote><br />\n如果佢一開始係顯示UAA你會唔會買?或者覺得件事有問題?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇交易signal睇volume睇圖<br />\n有機會買有機會唔買<br />\n唔一定"},{"pid":"3de606c28201b975d2ea4f84ca136ea794168201","tid":30253,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"報警"},{"pid":"cd8381ee5b3ba9ba84a158b69ecd48d1a8356205","tid":30253,"uid":10606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實成單野係無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但又真係有位入佢喎。。<br />\n<br />\n有位入緊係要入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身就唔會對報價付責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果一刻係買賣緊UA<br />\n而唔係UAA<br />\n亦都無諗過入UAA<br />\n而佢個報價系統亦顯示係UA</blockquote><br />\nOK 我明了<br />\n岩岩我搞錯左<br />\n<br />\n件事其實係咁<br />\n近日UA Class C (UA.C)改左代號轉左做 UA<br />\nUA Class A (UA) 就改左代號做 UAA<br />\n而睇個圖表 佢就咁寫係Under Armour咁即係代表買UA 既C Class<br />\n但個系統有問題 就照落左UA Class A</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以算係系統問題<br />\n對面都有提過美國出現問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但由出事到通知我相差接近16小時<br />\n好彩損失唔大<br />\n但都想SFC罰佢錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0560bbe2dbb0d2b75f8ba1d19140374f9c463e4","tid":30253,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:50:09.000Z","msg":"似系統問題<br />\n不過都搞大佢先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fc7b761600e428ff902f9cac625287e2c9fd2c","tid":30253,"uid":10606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似系統問題<br />\n不過都搞大佢先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 但點先可以搞到最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8484f2bc7cfc9eb5d51e3ab66d7844d9a2956daa","tid":30253,"uid":43111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似系統問題<br />\n不過都搞大佢先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下佢有冇出通告羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過佢系統唔update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276076339abfcd733